            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2005 00:00:00
            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ITERATOR_QUERY:"SELECT STRING_COLLECTION(PeakClass,source,sink,TransactionID,source_id,sink_id)\nFROM (SELECT DISTINCT I.AGREEMENT_TYPE AS PeakClass,\n                s1.service_point_name AS SOURCE,\n                s2.SERVICE_POINT_NAME AS Sink,\n                i.TRANSACTION_ID AS TransactionID,\n	s1.service_point_id AS source_id,\n	s2.service_point_id AS sink_id\n  FROM INTERCHANGE_TRANSACTION   i,\n       service_point             s1,\n       service_point             s2,\n       temporal_entity_attribute t\n WHERE i.AGREEMENT_TYPE LIKE '%FTR%'\n   AND i.CONTRACT_ID = :contract\n   AND t.ATTRIBUTE_ID =\n       (SELECT ATTRIBUTE_ID\n          FROM ENTITY_ATTRIBUTE\n         WHERE ATTRIBUTE_NAME = 'ClearedMW')\n   AND t.attribute_val <> '0'\n   AND (i.BEGIN_DATE = CASE\n           WHEN TO_NUMBER(to_char(:now, 'MM')) BETWEEN 1 AND 5 THEN\n            to_date('01-JUN-' || (to_char(:now, 'YYYY') - 1))\n           ELSE\n            TO_DATE('01-JUN-' || (to_char(:now, 'YYYY')))\n       END OR i.BEGIN_DATE = trunc(:now))\n   AND t.OWNER_ENTITY_ID = i.TRANSACTION_ID\n   AND s1.SERVICE_POINT_ID = i.SOURCE_ID\n   AND s2.SERVICE_POINT_ID = i.SINK_ID)
            IS_MULTICOLUMN:#1
            IDENT_COLUMNS:#4
            IS_INNER_LOOP:#1
            COMMENTS:"

            ITERATOR_QUERY:"SELECT STRING_COLLECTION(source,sink,node_id,sink_id)\nFROM (SELECT DISTINCT B.SERVICE_POINT_NAME AS SOURCE, \n	C.SERVICE_POINT_NAME AS sink,\n	B.SERVICE_POINT_ID AS node_id,\n	C.SERVICE_POINT_ID AS sink_id\n  FROM INTERCHANGE_TRANSACTION A, SERVICE_POINT B, SERVICE_POINT C\n WHERE A.CONTRACT_ID = :contract\n   AND A.TRANSACTION_TYPE IN ('Purchase')\n   AND a.commodity_id IN\n       (SELECT commodity_id\n          FROM it_commodity i\n         where i.commodity_name IN ('DayAhead Energy'))\n   AND A.SOURCE_ID = B.SERVICE_POINT_ID\n   AND A.SINK_ID = C.SERVICE_POINT_ID\n   AND A.SOURCE_ID <> A.SINK_ID)
            IS_MULTICOLUMN:#1
            IDENT_COLUMNS:#2

            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2000 00:00:00
            END_DATE:"
            ITERATOR_QUERY:"SELECT STRING_COLLECTION(node, node_id)\nFROM (SELECT DISTINCT S.SERVICE_POINT_NAME AS node, S.SERVICE_POINT_ID AS node_id\n       FROM SERVICE_POINT S, PJM_EMKT_PNODES P, INTERCHANGE_TRANSACTION T\n      WHERE T.CONTRACT_ID = :contract\n        AND S.EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER = TO_CHAR(P.PNODEID)\n        AND ((S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POD_ID AND\n            T.TRANSACTION_TYPE <> 'Sale') OR\n            (S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POR_ID AND T.TRANSACTION_TYPE = 'Sale')))
            IS_MULTICOLUMN:#1
            IDENT_COLUMNS:#1
            IS_INNER_LOOP:#0
            COMMENTS:"

begin object
    table_name:PRODUCT
    table_alias:PRODUCT
    PRODUCT_ID:*PRODUCT-0217
    PRODUCT_NAME:"PJM FTR Auction
    PRODUCT_ALIAS:"PJM FTR Auction
    PRODUCT_DESC:"PJM FTR Auction
    PRODUCT_EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER:"?
    PRODUCT_CATEGORY:"?
    BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2004 00:00:00
    END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
    ENTRY_DATE:@AUG-25-2004 13:08:26
    begin subtable
        table_name:EXTERNAL_SYSTEM_IDENTIFIER
        relationship:ENTITY_ID=PRODUCT_ID;ENTITY_DOMAIN_ID=-620
    end subtable
    begin subtable
        table_name:PRODUCT_COMPONENT
        relationship:PRODUCT_ID;BEGIN_DATE <= (DATE '2020-12-31' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND) AND NVL(END_DATE, DATE '9999-12-31') >= (DATE '2004-01-01' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND)
        begin row
            PRODUCT_ID:*PRODUCT-0217
            COMPONENT_ID:*COMPONENT-0013
            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2004 00:00:00
            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ENTRY_DATE:@AUG-17-2004 15:36:38
        end row
        begin row
            PRODUCT_ID:*PRODUCT-0217
            COMPONENT_ID:*COMPONENT-0014
            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2004 00:00:00
            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ENTRY_DATE:@AUG-25-2004 13:08:26
        end row
    end subtable

        relationship:COMPONENT_ID;BEGIN_DATE <= (DATE '2020-12-31' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND) AND NVL(END_DATE, DATE '9999-12-31') >= (DATE '2004-01-01' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND)

            COMPONENT_ID:*COMPONENT-0223
            SUB_COMPONENT_TYPE:"?
            SUB_COMPONENT_ID:#0
            ITERATOR_NAME:"node,node_id
            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2000 00:00:00
            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ITERATOR_QUERY:"SELECT STRING_COLLECTION(node, node_id)\n FROM (SELECT DISTINCT S.SERVICE_POINT_NAME as NODE, S.SERVICE_POINT_ID as NODE_ID \n  FROM SERVICE_POINT S, PJM_EMKT_PNODES P, INTERCHANGE_TRANSACTION T\n WHERE T.CONTRACT_ID = :contract\n   AND S.EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER = TO_CHAR(P.PNODEID)\n   AND ((S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POD_ID AND T.TRANSACTION_TYPE <> 'Sale') OR\n       (S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POR_ID AND T.TRANSACTION_TYPE = 'Sale'))\n   and t.commodity_id in\n       (select commodity_id\n          from it_commodity\n         where commodity_name in ('DayAhead Energy', 'RealTime Energy')))
            IS_MULTICOLUMN:#1
            IDENT_COLUMNS:#1
            IS_INNER_LOOP:#0
            COMMENTS:"
            ROW_NUMBER:#1
            ENTRY_DATE:@JUN-04-2010 14:39:53
        end row

            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ITERATOR_QUERY:"SELECT STRING_COLLECTION(node, node_id)\nFROM (SELECT DISTINCT S.SERVICE_POINT_NAME AS node, S.SERVICE_POINT_ID AS node_id\n  FROM SERVICE_POINT S, PJM_EMKT_PNODES P, INTERCHANGE_TRANSACTION T\n WHERE T.CONTRACT_ID = :contract\n   AND S.EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER = TO_CHAR(P.PNODEID)\n   AND ((S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POD_ID AND T.TRANSACTION_TYPE <> 'Sale') OR\n       (S.SERVICE_POINT_ID = T.POR_ID AND T.TRANSACTION_TYPE = 'Sale'))\n   and t.commodity_id in\n       (select commodity_id\n          from it_commodity\n         where commodity_name in ('DayAhead Energy', 'RealTime Energy')))

    table_alias:PRODUCT
    PRODUCT_ID:*PRODUCT-0261
    PRODUCT_NAME:"PJM Expansion Cost Recovery
    PRODUCT_ALIAS:"PJM Expansion Cost Recovery
    PRODUCT_DESC:"PJM Expansion Cost Recovery
    PRODUCT_EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER:"?
    PRODUCT_CATEGORY:"?
    BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2004 00:00:00
    END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
    ENTRY_DATE:@OCT-17-2006 16:19:08
    begin subtable
        table_name:EXTERNAL_SYSTEM_IDENTIFIER
        relationship:ENTITY_ID=PRODUCT_ID;ENTITY_DOMAIN_ID=-620
    end subtable
    begin subtable
        table_name:PRODUCT_COMPONENT
        relationship:PRODUCT_ID;BEGIN_DATE <= (DATE '2020-12-31' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND) AND NVL(END_DATE, DATE '9999-12-31') >= (DATE '2004-01-01' + INTERVAL '00' HOUR + INTERVAL '00' MINUTE + INTERVAL '00' SECOND)
        begin row
            PRODUCT_ID:*PRODUCT-0261
            COMPONENT_ID:*COMPONENT-0170
            BEGIN_DATE:@JAN-01-2004 00:00:00
            END_DATE:@DEC-31-2020 00:00:00
            ENTRY_DATE:@OCT-17-2006 16:19:08
        end row
    end subtable
end object
